LEFT JOIN (SELECT T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID, T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ, MAX (SBN_END_DATE) AS SBN_END_DATE FROM T_MANIFEST_ENTRY INNER JOIN T_MANIFEST_DETAIL ON T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SYSTEM_ID AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SEQ AND T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SBN_END_DATE IS NOT NULL WHERE T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.DELETE_FLG = 'false' AND NOT EXISTS( SELECT * FROM T_MANIFEST_DETAIL WHERE T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.DELETE_FLG = 'false' AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SYSTEM_ID AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SEQ and T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SBN_END_DATE IS NULL ) GROUP BY T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID, T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ UNION SELECT T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID, T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ, SBN_END_DATE FROM T_MANIFEST_ENTRY LEFT JOIN T_MANIFEST_DETAIL ON T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SYSTEM_ID AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SEQ WHERE T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.DELETE_FLG = 'false' and T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SBN_END_DATE IS NULL GROUP BY T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID, T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ, T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SBN_END_DATE )AS T_MANIFEST_D_GENPON_END ON T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID = T_MANIFEST_D_GENPON_END.SYSTEM_ID AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ = T_MANIFEST_D_GENPON_END.SEQ

LEFT JOIN (SELECT T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID, T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ, MAX (LAST_SBN_END_DATE) AS LAST_SBN_END_DATE FROM T_MANIFEST_ENTRY INNER JOIN T_MANIFEST_DETAIL ON T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SYSTEM_ID AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SEQ AND T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.LAST_SBN_END_DATE IS NOT NULL WHERE T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.DELETE_FLG = 'false' AND NOT EXISTS( SELECT * FROM T_MANIFEST_DETAIL WHERE T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.DELETE_FLG = 'false' AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SYSTEM_ID AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SEQ and T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.LAST_SBN_END_DATE IS NULL ) GROUP BY T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID, T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ UNION SELECT T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID, T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ, LAST_SBN_END_DATE FROM T_MANIFEST_ENTRY LEFT JOIN T_MANIFEST_DETAIL ON T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SYSTEM_ID AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ = T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.SEQ WHERE T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.DELETE_FLG = 'false' and T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.LAST_SBN_END_DATE IS NULL GROUP BY T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID, T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ, T_MANIFEST_DETAIL.LAST_SBN_END_DATE )AS T_MANIFEST_D_GENPON_LAST ON T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SYSTEM_ID = T_MANIFEST_D_GENPON_LAST.SYSTEM_ID AND T_MANIFEST_ENTRY.SEQ = T_MANIFEST_D_GENPON_LAST.SEQ
